Between 2007 and 2008, Amway was found guilty of illegal business practices in India, a ruling upheld by the Supreme Court of India and followed in 2021 by India's Enforcement Directorate attaching company and bank assets, identifying Amway's business model as a pyramid fraud and its product offerings a masquerade. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amway

item.title: A shameless use of kitten pictures to ask a favor
item.description:
Fostering kittens is one of two passions in my life. Here we have Vixen and Prancer, two of my newest foster kittens, being super cute. They already love my lap. But this post is about my second passion: my humanitarian trips to Guatemala.
I’ve been going three times a year since 2015, and we always go to the same village, Chuluc. So we have formed true, lasting, loving relationships with the villagers. I’m going on my 30th visit in three weeks. (Little Vixen here has already become a major lap-kitten, I am OBSESSED with her already)
But I want to talk about this woman, Josefina. I formed a deep connection with her on my first trip. She has a severe case of rheumatoid arthritis throughout her whole body, but is the most loving, selfless woman I’ve ever met. I love her like a sister, and call her my hermanita.
She is a single mom to her two daughters since her alcoholic, abusive husband left them five years ago. Her daughters Kely and Yasmin have to help her do everything - bathe, get dressed, walk, go to work, even eat. But they do all of it with no complaints and with love in their heart. (Yasmin was finishing a test when this pic was taken)
And Josefina has given them the greatest gift she is able to - she has scrimped and saved and sacrificed and has allowed her two girls to stay in school. This is no small feat in a community where 90% of children are taken out of school before fourth grade to work the fields or help around the house. She doesn’t smile much, but when she does, it lights up my heart
Kitten picture intermission. Dasher is so handsome! He’s got something going on in his left eye that we’ve gotta figure out though…
Her daughter Kely has recently graduated secondary school. She wants to be a nurse, and the income she will get will allow the whole family to get out of the cycle of poverty that they have been living in their whole lives.
Their house is literally on the side of a mountain, and with the degenerative disease Josefina has, it makes it almost impossible for her to get to the roadside peach stand she works at to make money. I stay with them at their house when I visit and even I have trouble getting to and from their home.
Josefina’s condition has deteriorated in the past two years. She will essentially be bed-bound this time next year. The only way we can keep her mobile is a very expensive surgery on her hips. $10,500 to be exact.
Our local community has rallied around this cause, but we are still very short of the goal. I’m throwing a Hail Mary here and reaching out to Imgur. I know you know me as KittensForDays, but to Josefina and her girls, I am simply Kati. And Kati desperately wants to be able to help her.
I’ll only do this once, and I know we’re heading into Christmas where money is tight, but I am asking anyone out there who can help out, to help out. https://gofund.me/f6f08afd1 I love this woman and she is such an inspiration to me. If I could fund her entire surgery, I would do it in a heartbeat.
I’m sorry I got deep in this post, but I’m desperate. Here’s a little palate cleanser for those of you who only want to see me as the Kitten Fosterer. Prancer keeps pushing her face against me and I am in HEAVEN. I won’t bring this up again, and kitten pics and videos (when Imgur will allow videos again) will be my focus again from here on out.
Thank you to anyone who made it this far. And now back to our regularly scheduled kitten pictures!! Little Dancer finally decided to settle down next to me. She’s got a ton of energy and hasn’t been super snuggly but I feel like the tide is changing haha
item.dc:creator: KittensForDays
